Phase 1 — Upload Anti-Deadlock Fix

FILES:
1. bookit/src/components/master/onboarding/OnboardingWizard.tsx (lines 173-187)
2. bookit/src/components/master/services/ImageUploader.tsx (lines 38-58)

TASK 1 — OnboardingWizard.tsx:
Replace lines 178-186 with:
```ts
try {
  const { data: up, error: upError } = await Promise.race([
    supabase.storage.from('images').upload(path, avatarFile, { upsert: true }),
    new Promise<never>((_, reject) =>
      setTimeout(() => reject(new Error('Timeout завантаження аватара')), 10_000)
    ),
